https://na.cx/i/knVwRUc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FknVwRUc.png&h=c0cc9364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>請問下LM狗，你可以解釋下咩叫重酬未呢？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你係街見到靚女食飯就鳩痕，周圍開po、開ig尋人我都算喇，最多當你係痴線佬，但你依家係講到明重酬喎，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">用利益誘使人做出不道德行為喎。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n依家人地食個飯咋喎，同你又咩關係都冇，你重酬尋人算係咩意思？江湖追殺令呀？<br />\n<br />\n如果有人為左錢而真係去用任何方法搵個女仔出黎，為左錢而去騷擾呢位女士，有冇諗過會對人地造成影響呀？<br />\n<br />\n人地食個飯就要比你件狗公騷擾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家你有名氣有地位大撚曬呀？成班盲粉為左追星造神，連基本道德都可以捨棄，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">到底係幾咁低賤嘅人先會做佢fans？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>麻煩LM狗呢次唔好再扮睇唔到，做返個男人啦，你一係出黎解釋，一係同人道歉。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9c834957a4d1530573739d14fe72afce5b76d58f","tid":2338542,"uid":161685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"大家樂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64d1eaefe015b92c785d22f05c8ae9b1f88024f","tid":2338542,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d23f0014ca51892f7e9085003c16d386b28f70","tid":2338542,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"你好快俾起底"},{"pid":"90aed175d61a064cf56343cbbd94755cb75946f4","tid":2338542,"uid":353860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:44:01.000Z",